thread.title: Jeff

author: Jeff
title: Jeff
text: Ordered my Ray-Ban sunglasses and took delivery the next day. Unfortunately I received a different model. Contacted customer service and instantly received return documents. Returned the package at a UPS access point nearby and by the time I got home, I received an e-mail confirming shipping of the correct model which arrived the next day. Despite initially receiving the wrong model the service and handlingspeed are excellent!
